Class CanonicizerPacket

java.lang.Object
  com.jgaap.gui.dnd.CanonicizerPacket

java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable
public class CanonicizerPacket
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable

This class essentially encapsulates a single CanonicizerLabel and any relevant transfer information as it is moved from one location in the GUI to another.
